summary:
- **Change to Underlying Benchmark Index Methodology**: Effective ~1 August 2025, the Markit iBoxx Global Developed Markets Liquid High Yield Capped Index (tracked by iShares Global High Yield Bond ETF, ASX:IHHY) will remove the 10% cap on TRACE-Eligible 144A bonds, expanding the investible universe.  
- **PDS Update**: Product Disclosure Statement for affected ETFs (including IHHY) will be reissued on the Effective Date.  

*No other material trading or capital markets information identified.*
